  "id": "RAW_04ef29",
  "title": "图像提供身份，文本定义一切！腾讯开源多模态视频定制工具 HunyuanCustom",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NDQwNTI0OQ==&mid=2247586763&idx=2&sn=5a542fab322018a2ec0b56787f0d42bf&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-09 09:36:00",
  "author": "AI科技大本营",
  "siteName": "AI科技大本营",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d329dbe-1ecd-4be8-4b36-9c0680fb5e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages __bg_gif wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.17647058823529413\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 578px;visibility: visible !important;height: 102px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"72\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d329dbe-1ecd-4be8-4b36-9c0680fb5e00/public\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理 | 梦依丹</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">出品丨AI 科技大本营（ID：rgznai100）</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在多模态视频生成技术逐渐成熟的今天，定制化能力成为衡量系统实用性的重要标准。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">5 月 8 日，腾讯混元团队正式推出并开源全新的多模态定制化视频生成框架 HunyuanCustom。该工具基于混元视频生成大模型（HunyuanVideo）打造，支持图像、文本、音频和视频等多种输入模态，提供高度可控且高质量的视频生成能力。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fac79177-0ac0-477e-090d-779a31394100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4872773536895674\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"786\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100103107\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fac79177-0ac0-477e-090d-779a31394100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e57b4b49-7fa9-4db6-6176-aac6e4990800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055306\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e57b4b49-7fa9-4db6-6176-aac6e4990800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态输入 + 主体一致性</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">解决定制视频「变脸难题」</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">传统图生视频或文生视频模型虽可合成视觉内容，但通常难以在更换动作、背景、服饰等条件下，保持人物身份不变——比如人物“变脸”、物体“漂移”等问题较为常见。HunyuanCustom 的核心目标正是解决这一挑战。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">HunyuanCustom 引入了基于 LLaVA 的图文融合模块，结合时间级联的图像 ID 增强机制，使视频在全程保持“主体一致”。在此基础上，HunyuanCustom 进一步支持音频驱动和视频驱动等多模态控制输入，实现场景中的声音联动、角色替换等更复杂的定制任务。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfeae1a4-f051-4158-6385-529b2450e000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/VeJKXItpwPUm5xcy5WGYOpjibickgIdmSbDpOKvZdQ9B7J2hD8iaPicZyV1JlGHlSgOeGIWGHx8rTY6T7S6lbchhnA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100103109\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfeae1a4-f051-4158-6385-529b2450e000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">HunyuanCustom 整体框架，支持基于文本、图像、音频和视频等条件生成主体一致性视频</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">HunyuanCustom 支持文本、图像、音频和视频等多种输入形式。简单来说，你可以上传一张或多张人物或物体的照片，为一个或多个主体生成定制化的视频内容；也可以配上一段音频，让视频中的人物“开口说话”或唱歌。更进一步，它还支持视频输入，能将已有视频中的指定对象，精准替换为用户上传的目标图像，实现个性化内容植入。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3978971164071641098\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3978971164071641098\" data-vidtype=\"5\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbTibHzVRJvm0xmdYhEmMnib2gslclSbZKMbnU9DO7DKoM4zeQFv61avRcTRH2fvaXibcLXVFbmcQbYgw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.8990654205607476\" data-w=\"2032\"></iframe></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c97bff1b-06ca-46b1-9b8c-4c751e115400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055305\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c97bff1b-06ca-46b1-9b8c-4c751e115400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">身份增强 + 模态解耦注入机制</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">在数据构建方面，团队引入了 Qwen、YOLO、InsightFace、GroundingSAM2 等模型协同构建数据标签体系，覆盖人类、动物、植物、建筑、动画等多个主体类型。训练中采用 Flow Matching 框架，结合结构化标注和 mask 增强策略，显著提升了模型泛化能力与编辑灵活度。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，为实现可控与一致性的统一，HunyuanCustom 在系统架构上设计了多个关键模块：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">LLaVA 图文交互模块：引入文本与图像模板融合机制，使描述词与身份图像协同表达；</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">图像 ID 增强模块：利用 3D-VAE 和 RoPE 时间嵌入机制，在时间维度传播身份特征；</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">AudioNet 模块：通过空间交叉注意力实现分层音频对齐，支持多级语音表达；</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">视频驱动注入模块：基于 patchify 的特征对齐网络，实现视频 latent 与身份注入的融合。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">上述模块使 HunyuanCustom 可在训练与推理阶段均实现图像、语音、视频等模态的解耦控制，为多模态生成提供了灵活接口。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5babfca6-97d0-42f7-c02e-4377a7635e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055307\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5babfca6-97d0-42f7-c02e-4377a7635e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">性能表现：多任务超越现有开源模型</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为了验证 HunyuanCustom 的实际效果，腾讯团队将其与多款主流视频定制方法进行了对比测试，包括 VACE、Skyreels、Pika、Vidu、Keling 和 Hailuo 等。评估指标涵盖了 人脸/主体一致性（Face-Sim）、视频与文本的一致性（CLIP-B-T）、图像语义相似性（DINO-Sim）、时间一致性（Temp-Consis）以及整体视频质量打分（DD）。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23febd00-8cfb-4a4e-b602-51bf6815ea00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43123209169054444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"698\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100103111\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23febd00-8cfb-4a4e-b602-51bf6815ea00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从测试结果来看，HunyuanCustom 在主体一致性（0.627）方面显著领先其他模型，视频的视觉连贯性和主体特征保留更为优秀。在语义层面，DINO-Sim 得分也达到 0.593，处于当前开源方案中的领先水平。同时，在保持较高时间一致性的前提下，其整体视频质量评分（DD）达 0.71，平衡了稳定性与细节表现。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，HunyuanCustom 的单主体生成能力已在混元官网上线，用户可以在“模型广场-图生视频-参考生视频”中体验，其他能力将于 5 月内陆续对外开源。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">体验入口：https://hunyuan.tencent.com/modelSquare/home/play?modelId=192</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">项目官网：https://hunyuancustom.github.io/</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">代码仓库：https://github.com/Tencent/HunyuanCustom</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">技术报告：https://arxiv.org/pdf/2505.04512</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d5bfdb5-ab2b-4014-9c7b-64d8b7fe1d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055310\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d5bfdb5-ab2b-4014-9c7b-64d8b7fe1d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63ecf59e-6fac-4047-d83a-f1d86f3ce100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100103114\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63ecf59e-6fac-4047-d83a-f1d86f3ce100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯开源多模态视频定制工具 HunyuanCustom，支持图像、文本、音频和视频输入，解决主体一致性问题，并已对外开源",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯开源多模态视频定制工具 HunyuanCustom，支持图像、文本、音频和视频输入，解决主体一致性问题，并已对外开源",
  "summary": "5 月 8 日，腾讯混元团队正式推出并开源多模态定制化视频生成框架 HunyuanCustom。该工具基于混元视频生成大模型，支持图像、文本、音频和视频等多种输入模态，通过 LLaVA 图文融合模块和时间级联的图像 ID 增强机制，解决了传统视频生成中主体一致性的问题。HunyuanCustom 在主体一致性、语义相似性和视频质量等多项指标测试中领先其他开源模型，支持角色替换、音频驱动等复杂定制化场景。文章详细说明了其技术架构、数据构建方法、关键模块设计以及性能表现，并提供了体验入口和开源链接。",
